    • Constructor Detail

      • Request

        public Request(java.lang.String name,
               java.lang.String info,
               Room preferred_room,
               int e,
               java.lang.String status,
               boolean b,
               java.lang.String time,
               java.lang.String start_date,
               java.lang.String end_date)
        Parameters:
        name - String that stores the name of the Student who made the request
        info - String that stores the purpose for which the room needs to be booked.
        preferred_room - String that has the preferred room a student wants to book
        e - An integer denoting the expected audience
        status - String that stores the status of the request
        b - Boolean value that denotes whether the student is notified when the request gets accepted
        time - String that stores the time at which the request was made. Stores the date in "yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss" format
        start_date - Stores the start date and time of the event. Stores the date in "yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss" format
        end_date - Stores the end date and time of the event. Stores the date in "yyyy/MM/dd HH:mm:ss" format
